These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, cherry, kale, corn, asparagus, pepper, nectarine
There are 7 different nationalities: british, canadian, nigerian, indonesian, italian, turkish, thai
 1. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating corn is not the turkish##6
 3. the british is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the thai is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 6. the british is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 7. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the canadian##7
 8. the canadian is on the left of the thai##1
 9. the indonesian is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the nigerian##7
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the british##3
11. the italian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
13. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
14. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
15. the person eating asparagus is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | kale    | pear    | cherry | pepper | corn | asparagus    | nectarine |
| Nationality   | italian | british | nigerian  | turkish   | indonesian    | canadian | thai |

