.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pepper, carrot, garlic, strawberry, kale, raspberry, pear
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, traveling, sudoku, video-games, reading, collecting, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating carrot##7
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating strawberry##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
 6. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
 7. the person eating kale is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the person eating carrot##7
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
10. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person eating pear##6
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person eating strawberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | pear  | garlic | raspberry | strawberry | pepper     | kale | carrot  |
| Hobby   | sudoku | collecting | traveling  | drawing  | reading | video-games      | writing |

