 5. the fan of punk is between the fan of r&b and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 6. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the fan of soul and the fan of pop##7
10. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
11. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is photography is not the fan of punk##6
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is photography##7
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
15. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
16. the person who's hobby is photography is not the fan of r&b##6
17. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
18. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
19. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5

