 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person driving the train##7
 8. the person who's sport is airplaneing is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is soccer##7
12. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
14. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
