 9. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
10. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
13. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the scooter##7
14. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the taxi##1
15. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is parkour##1
16. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
